West Virginia Society of Osteopathic Medicine, annual general practice update, The Greenbrier, White Sulphur Springs, W Va. Contact Charlotte Ann Pulliam, exec dir, WVSOM, PO Box 5266, Charleston, WV 25361-0266 (304) 345-9836.<BR>
