<h1>CHAPTER 1<h/1>
<pre>

</pre>
<h1>AN INTRODUCTION TO MARKETING</h1><p>
<p>
<pre>

</pre>
<ol>
<h2><li> What is marketing?<br>
   What are its origins?<br>  
   What does marketing mean to our          
  modern society?<p>

<li> What are the key foundation concepts  
   of marketing?<p>

<li>Why is it important to study                   
 marketing?<p>

<li>Why is marketing still evolving?
   How is it evolving?<p>

<li> What are the marketing mix variables   
   (4 Ps)?<br>
   How do marketers use the 4Ps to           
  satisfy consumers and achieve               
organizational goals?<br><p></h2>

</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT12-B22-31</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA044-000795-B021-205</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
