<title>Roots & Stems</title>

</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<center>
<a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/techdirect/maps/techdrbr.map"><img border=0 src="/techdirect/gifs/techdrbr.gif" ismap></a><br>
<img src="/techdirect/gifs/mprule.gif"><P>
</center>
<a href="gifs/roots.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_roots.gif"></a>
<BR>
<h2>Roots & Stems</h2>
<h4>Hybrid Windows/Mac #34466</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr>
<a href="gifs/roots1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_roots1.gif"></a>
<br>
<i>Roots & Stems</i>: This program discusses: functions of the root; primary and secondary roots;
tap root system; fibrous root system; adventitious root system; root cap; growth zones; root
tissues; functions of the stem; types of stems; tissues of herbaceous monocot, herbaceous
dicot and woody dicot stems.
<br clear=right>
