<title>Birds: Characteristics & Adaptations</title>

</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<center>
<a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/techdirect/maps/techdrbr.map"><img border=0 src="/techdirect/gifs/techdrbr.gif" ismap></a><br>
<img src="/techdirect/gifs/mprule.gif"><P>
</center>

<a href="gifs/birdmain.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_birdmain.gif"></a>
<BR>
<h2>Birds: Characteristics & Adaptations</h2>
<h4>Hybrid Windows/Mac #34457</h4>
<i>Birds: Characteristics & Adaptations</i>: This colorful program explores the evolution,
structure, and adaptations of birds in an extensive and insightful manner.  Topics include: the
classification of birds; birds relation to dinosaurs; flight; feathers; wing types and migration;
Darwin's finches; adaptation and beaks; adaptation and feet; digestive system; excretory
system; respiratory system; reproductive system; nervous system.

