<a href="gifs/mosbycv.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_mosbycv.gif"></a><P>
<BR><P>

<h2>Mosby's Medical Encyclopedia CD-ROM</h2><P>
<h4>Windows CD-ROM #35056</h4><BR>
<BR clear=left>
<HR><P>

<a href="gifs/mosby1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=20 src="smgifs/s_mosby1.gif"></a><P>

<I>Mosby's Medical Encyclopedia </I>is the quickest way to get accurate, up-to-date medical information. From symptoms and diseases to treatments, procedures and complete drug entries, it's exactly what students need to access vital health care information. Students can browse through the encyclopedia using the alphabetic tabs, or they can use the powerful search feature to quickly locate a specific topic. Students can cut, paste, or print information into reports, take notes with an on-screen notepad, or save their place with the electronic bookmarks.  <P>
<BR clear=right>

<a href="gifs/mosby2.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_mosby2.gif"></a><P>

This collection features over 70 full-color  illustrations of all major body systems.  Students will marvel at the detailed drawings of skeletal, muscular, circulatory systems and more&#139;with all body parts labeled with proper medical terminology.  <P>
<BR clear=left>

<a href="gifs/mosby3.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=20 src="smgifs/s_mosby3.gif"></a><P>

Other features include:<BR>
<UL>
<LI>Nearly 20,000 entries and 1,200 illustrations<BR>
<LI>4,000 audio pronunciations of key medical terms<BR>
<LI>20 Health care Appendixes<BR>
<LI>Detailed atlas of human anatomy<BR>
<LI>Complete guide to prescription and over the counter drugs<BR>
<LI>Listing of health organizations<BR>
<LI>Leading health problem appendix<BR>
</UL>
<BR clear=right>

