<H2>INFOPEDIA CD-ROM</H2><P>
<H4>Windows CD-ROM #29167</H4><BR>
<BR clear=left>
<HR><P>

<a href="gifs/infopd1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_infopd1.gif"></a><P>

No library on earth stimulates the imagination quite like INFOPEDIA.  This powerful multimedia resource makes learning fun with eight different reference works, including a 29-volume encyclopedia, over 200,000 entries, full-motion 150 videos and animations, over 5,000 photographs, 2,100 maps, flags, charts, and tables, 450 recordings and narrations.  All of these features are linked through a choice of search methods designed to gather and organize information in the way you'd like to see it.  <P>
<BR clear=right>

<a href="gifs/infopd2.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_infopd2.gif"></a><P>

Discover the sights, sounds and thoughts of the world through the 29-volume Funk & Wagnall's New Encyclopedia, Roget's 21st Century Thesaurus, Hammond World Atlas, The World Almanac of Facts, Merriam-Webster's Dictionary of English Usage, and Webster's New Biographical Dictionary.<BR>
