<head>

<title>Mendel's Principles of Heredity</title>

</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<center>
<a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/techdirect/maps/techdrbr.map"><img border=0 src="/techdirect/gifs/techdrbr.gif" ismap></a><br>
<img src="/techdirect/gifs/mprule.gif"><P>
</center>

<a href="gifs/mendels.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_mend.gif"></a>
<BR>
<h2>Mendel's Principles of Heredity</h2>

<h4>Hybrid Windows/Mac #34455</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr>
<a href="gifs/mend1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_mend1.gif"></a>
Mendel's Principles of Heredity: An interesting and informative presentation that contains: a
biography on Mendel; Mendel's pure-breeding pea plant; self-fertilizing pea plants; the seven
famous traits of Mendel's pea plants; Mendel's experiment on the inheritance of seed color;
modern terms in genetics; heredity based probabilities; Mendel's law of segregation; the
punnett square; Mendel's law of 
independent assortment.
