<a href="gifs/hlthwell.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_hlthwell.gif"></a>
<BR>
<h2>Health & Wellness Videodisc</h2>

<h4>Videodisc #15095</h4>

<BR clear=left>
<HR>
Enhance your classroom with Brown & Benchmark's <EM>Health and Wellness Videodisc</EM>. This
easy-to-use videodisc allows you to enhance your classroom lectures and discussions for
health and wellness courses through the use of valuable images.  This videodisc includes over
1,500 images providing you with a large resource for classroom presentation. <P>
 
Each image is listed, described and barcoded in the accompanying Instructor's
Manual to facilitate the development of your presentations.  <P>

The <I>Health and Wellness</I> <EM>Videodisc</EM> is easy-to-use, and is centered around traditional health
and wellness topics, including:
<UL>
