<BR>This stimulating program combines live action photography, breathtaking footage from space,
artwork, and three-dimensional models to present an exciting introduction to our solar
system.  <i>Exploring Our Solar System</i> looks at every planet in our solar system, along with
each planet's moons.  The program also covers, in detail, the composition and movements of
asteroids, comets, and meteors.  Also covered are theories on the origin of the solar system,
life on other planets, and the  existence of other solar systems in the universe.  

