<h2>World History CD-ROM</h2>

<h4>Windows CD-ROM #34370</h4>
<h4>(Windows Only)</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr><a href="gifs/world1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_world1.gif"></a>
From the beginning of time mankind believed recording the events of their day essential to
the development and evolution of human civilization. Due to the  human instinct to teach,
historical literature and artifacts have been preserved by philosophers, scholars, historians,
artists, devouts in religion and politics, authors, and institutions of greater learning.
This multimedia encyclopedia preserves history for future generations through diversely
selected texts, narrations, audio-enriched animations and maps, presidential biographies,
photographs, still graphics and moving pictures. 
