<html>

<head>
<title>MedWorks</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<center>

<a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/techdirect/maps/techdrbr.map"><img border=0 src="/techdirect/gifs/techdrbr.gif" ismap></a><br><img src="/techdirect/gifs/mprule.gif"><br>

</center>
<BR>
<a href="gifs/medcover.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_medcover.gif"></a>

<H2>MedWorks CD-ROM</H2>

<h4>Windows CD-ROM #33639</h4>
<h4>(Windows Only)</h4>

<BR clear=left>
<hr>
<a href="gifs/med2.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_med2.gif"></a><BR>

<I>MedWorks Anatomy & Physiology</I> is an interactive, multimedia training course in human anatomy and physiology.  For each system of the human body, this course presents beautifully rendered, color 3D illustrations accompanied by descriptive text.  Press a key to pop-up balloon text for a deeper explanation of details in the illustrations or to call up human voice pronunciations of over 2,000 selected terms. 

<a href="gifs/med3.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_med3.gif"></a><P>

 This remarkable program is divided into 20 lessons, each lesson includes 3D color illustration, text, and exercises that include multiple choice, true/false, and fill-in-the-blank questions.  Pre- and Post-tests measure results for overall performance.  

<a href="gifs/medwk1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_medwk1.gif"></a><P>

The chapters/lessons are as follows:<BR>
Anatomy and Physiology Overview / Body Chemistry / Cells and Tissues / Integumentary System / Skeletal System / The Muscular System / Nervous System / Central Nervous System / Peripheral Nervous System / Somatic and Autonomic Nervous System / Sensory Organs / Endocrine System / Cardiovascular System: The Blood / Cardiovascular System: The Heart / Lymphatic and Immune Systems / Respiratory System / Digestive System / Urinary System / Reproductive System / Inheritance.<P>

<a href="gifs/medwk4.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 <a src="smgifs/s_medwk4.gif"></a>

Chapter tests follow completion of each lesson.  The automatically scored quiz and chapter test results may be easily viewed for quick progress checks throughout the course.  The <I>MedWorks A&P Workbook</I> mirrors the software course material and serves as a lesson-by-lesson study guide as well as a reference source. <P>

<a href="gifs/medwk5.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_medwk5.gif"></a>

A complete dictionary alphabetically lists each term covered in the CD-ROM and breaks down the word by components for easy comprehension.  Students can hear each term pronounced with the touch of a key.<P>

<B>Study Guide/Workbook<BR>
$30.00 (#33641)<BR>
</B>

