<h2>American Vista CD-ROM</h2>

<h4>Windows CD-ROM #34510</h4>
<h4>Macintosh CD-ROM #34582</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr><a href="gifs/amvist1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_amvist1.gif"></a>
This interactive atlas of the United States is more than just maps.  American Vista gives the
user a taste of the diverse culture and landscape of America.  View color photos of the
Grand Canyon or the Coast of Maine, listen to examples of regional dialects comparing the
accent of a man from the mountains of North Carolina with one from the upper peninsula of
Michigan. Hear the music of this great nation as you listen to the blues of Chicago or a
Hawaiian prayer chant.  <P>

<a href="gifs/amvist3.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_amvist3.gif"></a><P>
Detailed maps illustrate the topography, natural resources, and environmental and
geopolitical features of the country.  A time line of important events and the text and
narration of significant documents like the Declaration of Independence and the Constitution
are included.

