<a href="gifs/atlascv.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_atlascv.gif"></a>
<BR>
<h2>World Vista CD-ROM</h2>

<h4>Windows CD-ROM #34578</h4>
<h4>Macintosh CD-ROM #34579</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr><a href="gifs/atlas4.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_atlas4.gif"></a>
Get to know the amazing world we live in and its diverse people with <I>World Vista!</I> This
interactive atlas of the world contains more than just maps.  It provides easy access to a rich
multimedia environment of information, searchable facts, pictures and audio clips that
illustrate the diversity of the world's people and nations. Its cross-referenced data lets the     
student instantly put demographic, political and economic data in perspective.  Students also
can print maps and text or copy them into reports or presentations.  
<a href="gifs/atlas5.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_atlas5.gif"></a><P>
Additional features include: 
The latest detailed maps from Rand McNally, cross referenced facts and statistics, more than
1,000 color photographs, and examples, music, and 25 standard phrases spoken in languages
representing more than 200 of the world's nations.
Easy-to-use interface is designed for maximum performance from CD-ROM

