<center>
<h2>Interactive Multimedia<br> Biology<br><p> CD-ROM Series</h2></center>
<br clear=left>
<hr><p>
Fascinate and develop your students' understanding of key biological concepts with this series
of "real" CD-ROM multimedia biology programs. The Interactive Multimedia Biology Series
provides complete, accurate, and up-to-date information in an interesting and highly
motivational manner.  Flexible and individualized instruction is achieved through a variety of
learning experiences, instructional approaches and options.  Appropriate for use by one  
student, a group of students, or teacher with the entire classroom. Each program is a      
complete stand-alone course on a specific biological subject.  
<p>
This courseware includes sophisticated animations and special effects that are used in an
instructional manner; hands-on interactive tutorials; motivational sound effects; high quality
narrations; brand new scripts containing current scientific concepts and theories.  Plus,   
program operation is extremely user-friendly, a feature teachers and students will appreciate.  
<p>
Each CD-ROM includes a user-friendly interface; a narrated presentation that covers the  
subject area in a thorough and informative manner; interactive tutorials that help to reinforce
concepts; online help; a pretest to test students knowledge before the presentation; a post-test
for students to take after the presentation; and an online glossary that allows students to
instantly access a list of key terms presented in the program.
<p>
<center>
