<h2>American Goverment CD-ROM</h2>

<h4>Windows CD-ROM #23460</h4>
<h4>Macintosh CD-ROM #23459</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr><a href="gifs/gov1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_gov1.gif"></a>
Brown & Benchmark Publishers provides an exciting journey for students of political
science. This CD-ROM makes it easy for students to navigate through study, practice and
application of political concepts.  The combination of text, video, audio and graphics involve
students in the learning process by giving them the option of accessing reference material,
learning through games, or taking a quiz and receiving feedback.  <EM>American Government</EM>
will involve students in the interrelationships between the rules, the strategies and players
that impact the political game
<P>

<a href="gifs/gov2.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_gov2.gif"></a><P>

Students can jump into the interactive time outs at any point during the session to relate to
the written text material. It also asks users to think critically about a question or issue.
