<h2>Explorations in Human Biology CD-ROM</h2>

<h4>Windows CD-ROM #22963</h4>
<h4>Macintosh CD-ROM #22964</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr><a href="gifs/humbio2.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_humbio2.gif"></a>
<BR>Now your students can explore human biology through movement, color, sound, and
interaction.  This set of 16 interactive explorations from Wm. C. Brown Publishers allows
students to set variables and then evaluate results.  This program features colorful, precisely
labeled graphics and animated illustrations, with English and Spanish narration.

<a href="gifs/humbio3.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_humbio3.gif"></a><p>

