<HEAD>
<TITLE>BodyWorks 5.0</TITLE>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><P>

<center><P>
<a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/techdirect/maps/techdrbr.map"><img border=0 src="/techdirect/gifs/techdrbr.gif" ismap></a><br><img src="/techdirect/gifs/mprule.gif"><br><P>
</center><P>
<a href="gifs/bodycvii.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_bodycvii.gif"></a><P>
<BR><P>
<B>BodyWorks 5.0 CD-ROM</B><P>
Windows CD-ROM #36171<BR>
Macintosh CD-ROM #36172<P>
<BR clear=left>
<hr><P>

<a href="gifs/bodywks1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_bodywks1.gif"></a><P>

<I>BodyWorks 5.0</I> is the ultimate multimedia reference guide to human anatomy and physiology.  Tour the human body through text, movies, 3D models and animation.  View every layer of the body  - skin, fatty tissue, muscles, skeleton, internal organs, and the organs and systems within that layer.  Take a tour of the heart, lungs, digestive system and more. It's all there in full color at the touch of a button.<P>
<BR clear=right>

<a href="gifs/bodywks2.gif"><img border=2 align=left hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_bodywks2.gif"></a>

<I>BodyWorks 5.0</I> is designed to let students learn about the body at their own pace or to provide a more structured educational experience in the form of fact-filled lessons and the multimedia classroom.  Two exciting additions to this version are Dr. BodyWorks, the multimedia classroom featuring 3D animated lectures, and BodyBasics, an exciting, fast paced anatomy and physiology game show. <P>
<BR clear=left>

<a href="gifs/bodywks3.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_bodywks3.gif"></a>

Other features include:<BR>
<UL>
<LI>Comprehensive overview of all major body systems<BR>
<LI>40 minutes of full-action 256-color video and animations in over 50 movies<BR>
<LI>25 fully rendered virtual reality 3D models<BR>
<LI>Over 300,000 words of text <BR>
<LI>On-line glossary with over 1,200 medical terms<BR>
<LI>Pronunciations of 1,900 terms<BR>
<LI>Peel-Away layered 3D reality human body<BR>
<LI>Quizzes and lessons on major body systems<BR>
</UL>
<BR clear=right>

NEW student workbook now FREE with each CD-ROM!<BR>
Inside BodyWorks: A Student Guide to BodyWorks. Inside BodyWorks is a great new  student workbook designed to enhance student understanding of anatomy and   physiology in health, biology and anatomy and physiology course work.  It contains:<BR>
<UL>
<LI>content background with the fundamental ideas<BR>
<LI>exercises to guide the student through the CD ROM<BR>
<LI>critical thinking to apply knowledge to clinical problems<BR>
<LI>integrating science using all sciences<BR>
</UL>
<BR clear=left>

