<h2>Atlas of U.S. Presidents CD-ROM</h2>

<h4>Windows CD-ROM #34580</h4>
<h4>Macintosh CD-ROM #34581</h4>
<BR clear=left>
<hr><a href="gifs/pres1.gif"><img border=2 align=right hspace=15 vspace=10 src="smgifs/s_pres1.gif"></a>
Portraits, cross-referenced facts and biographies for each of the 42 presidents of the United
States can be accessed from an easy-to-use visual interface.  Audio clips of important public
speeches are available for each president from Theodore Roosevelt through Bill Clinton. 
Readings of speeches by George Washington, Thomas Jefferson and Abraham Lincoln are
also included.  The <EM>Atlas of U.S. Presidents</EM> also offers summaries of election results and
portraits and biographies of each first lady.  Users can print the illustration, description and
facts or copy them into reports.  


