<title>ITD Computing Resources</title>
<link rev="made" href="mailto:www@itd.nrl.navy.mil">
<h1>NRL<IMG SRC=../GIF/NRLlogo.xbm ALT=" ">ITD<p>
Naval Research Laboratory<br>
Information Technology Division</h1>
<h1>ITD Computing Resources</h1>
<h2>Computers</h2>
ITD has hundreds of workstations and personal computers linked
by an extensive network.  Many of these machines are in specialized
facilities.
Most of these resources belong to the various branches and are used
primarily for work performed within those branches.
A few more widely available resources are listed here.
Follow the hyperlinks for more information.
<ul>
<li><i>itd.nrl.navy.mil</i> is a system operated by
and in support of the Division as a whole.  Users of this system
can access
<a href="../SYS/itd.html">local documentation</a>.
Persons who have a relationship with the Division can request
an account by sending e-mail to
<em>accounts@itd.nrl.navy.mil</em>.
<li>NRL's backbone fiber optic network, much of NRL's "big iron", and
a Visualization Laboratory are
operated by Code 5590, the <a href="http://www.nrl.navy.mil/ccs.html">Center
for Computational Science</a>.
These resources
are used by researchers from all parts of NRL as well as from outside NRL.
<li>A Virtual Reality Laboratory is operated by Code 5580, the
<a href="http://www.ait.nrl.navy.mil/about-ait.html">Advanced Information Technology Branch</a>.
</ul>
<h2>Internet Domains</h2>
<dl>
<dt><i>nrl.navy.mil</i>
<dd>The primary domain for computers at NRL.
Some ITD computers (mostly operated by codes
<a href="http://www.nrl.navy.mil/ccs.html">5592, 5594, and 5595</a>)
have names in this domain, but most ITD machines are instead
in one of the following subdomains.
Each subdomain below has a primary machine whose name is the same as
the name of the subdomain.  (For historical reasons, a few other machines
in the subdomains have aliases in <i>nrl.navy.mil</i>.)
<dt><i>aic.nrl.navy.mil</i>
<dd><a href="http://www.aic.nrl.navy.mil">Code 5510</a>.
<dt><i>ait.nrl.navy.mil</i>
<dd><a href="http://www.ait.nrl.navy.mil/about-ait.html">Code 5580</a>.
<dt><i>cmf.nrl.navy.mil</i>
<dd><a href="http://www.nrl.navy.mil/ccs.html">Code 5590, especially 5591 and 5593</a>.
<dt><i>itd.nrl.navy.mil</i>
<dd>All other Codes within the Division.
</dl>
<p>
A few other subdomains are managed by other parts of NRL.
<hr>
<a href="../"><i>Visit ITD Home Page</i></a>
<p>
Address comments and questions to
<EM><a href="mailto:www@itd.nrl.navy.mil">www@itd.nrl.navy.mil</a></EM>.
