Eurographics 94
<P>

The major general theme computer graphics conference in Europe.  It
is preceded by several Eurographics' sponsored workshops.  My
understanding is that the Eurographics Workshop on Virtual
Environments, begun last year after discussions between myself and
Eurographics officials and cosponsored by ONR Europe, will be a two
day workshop preceding the conference in Oslo and will be largely
sponsored by the European Commission.  Eurographics 92 was the
first event I attended in Europe after arriving ONREUR and was
described in <a href="rosenblum.001.html">REALIZATION REPORT #1</a>.
<P>

<PRE>
	12-16 Sept. 1994
</PRE>
	Oslo, Norway
	Contact: eg94@si.sintef.no
