<ul>

<li> <a href=http://www.ndf.rl.af.mil/~accord/stp6.html>STP-6 Satellite Communications</a>
<li> <a href=http://www.ndf.rl.af.mil/~accord/stp8.html>STP-8 Terrestrial Communications</a>
<li> STP-9 C3 Systems Technology
<li> <a href=http://www.ndf.rl.af.mil/~accord/stp10.html>STP-10 Distributed Information Systems Technology</a>
<li> STP-11 Secure Information Systems <i>(where you are now)</i>
<li> <a href=http://www.ndf.rl.af.mil/~accord/>ACCORD Task Force</a>; 
<a href=http://www.itr.unisa.edu.au/~dstowww/>Australian site for ACCORD and some other things</a>
</ul>
<H3>The former Subgroup X</H3>
<ul>
<li> XTP-1 Trustworthy Computing Technology
<li> XTP-2 Software Engineering
<li> XTP-3 Computer Architecture
<li> XTP-4 Machine Intelligence
