<p>

<h4>CONTACT INFORMATION</h4>

The telephone number for the adminstrative office is: <b>(202) 767-2389</b>.
<P>
  
Our fax number is: <b>(202) 404-7942</b>. <P>  

The mailing address is:
<p>
   <b>Naval Research Laboratory<br>
   Code 5540<br>
   4555 Overlook Ave., SW<br>
   Washington, D.C.  20375-5337</b><br>
<p>

<hr>

<h4>VISIT REQUEST  INFORMATION</h4><p>

Security clearances can be faxed to NRL's Security Office at: <b>(202) 767-3990</b>.<p>

Or mailed to the following address:
<p>
<b>Naval Research Laboratory<br>
Attn:  Security/Visitor Control<br>
4555 Overlook Ave., SW<br>
Washington, D.C.  20375-5337</b><br><p>

To verify that clearances have been received, call: <b>(202) 767-2996</b> or <b>(202) 767-6924</b>.<p>

