<head>
<title>ORGANIZATION OF CODE 5540</title>
</head>
<body>
The Center, directed by 
<a href="personnel/mclean.html">
 John McLean</a>, comprises six sections:

<ul>
  <li> Communication Security (Code 5541)
  <li><a href="5542/hp-txt.html">
       Computer Security (Code 5542)</a> 
  <li><a href="5543/hp-txt.html">
       Formal Methods (Code 5543)</a>
  <li><a href="http://tonnant.itd.nrl.navy.mil/5544.html">
       Network Security (Code 5544)</a>
  <li>INFOSEC Facilities Section (Code 5545)
  <li> Software Engineering Section (Code 5546)
</ul>

<p>
<hr>
