<head>
<Title>Developing High Assurance Building Blocks</Title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#0000FF" vlink="#871F78" alink="#FF0000">

<IMG SRC="../gifs/DHABBlogo.GIF">

<HR>
<p>
This page is part of the web at the
<a href="../index.html">
 Center for High Assurance Computer Systems</a>.
<p>
<HR>

<H2>Mission</H2>

Developing new approaches, including the use of formal
specifications and automated reasoning tools, for designing,
implementing, and verifying software/hardware building blocks that can
be certified to enforce specified critical properties with a high
degree of assurance.

