Semi-annual progress rept. 1 Jan-30 June 76, Honeywell Information 
Systems Inc Mclean Va Federal Systems Operations
NTIS AD-A038 261/4
/security/verification/Security Kernel/Multics. 

Adleman, N.; Gilson, J. R.; Sestak, R. J.; Ziller, R. J. Semi-Annual 
Progress Report July 1975 to December 1975. 1976 Jan. 
Honeywell Information Systems Inc Mclean Va Federal Systems 
