Douglas, I. J. Audit and Control of Systems Software. 1984. 
NCC Publications
0-85012-400-X
This book considers the security aspects of large mainframe systems. 
The first part is an overview of the components of a general system, 
and the security problems likely to occur in connection with each. The 
second part is a series of articles of experiences in particular large 
systems, from different manufacturers. The overview is quite short and 
simplified, but the practical articles give useful pointers to likely 
problems.
