Fine, T.; Haigh, J. T.; O'Brien, R. C.; Toups, D. L. (Honeywell). 
Noninterference and Unwinding for LOCK. in: Proceedings Computer 
Security Foundations Workshop; 1989 Jun 11; Franconia, New 
