security needs include physical protection, operational integrity, 
secrecy of intentions, capabilities and knowledge. A major problem is 
that of false information or orders via its sensors or communications 
links. The paper categorises the generic threat types and attempts to 
stimulate interest in a field not directly related to the problems of 
multilevel security.
