Gasser, Morrie; Goldstein, Andy; Kaufman, Charlie; Lampson, Butler 
(Digital Equipment Corporation). The Digital Distributed System 
Security Architecture. in: 12th National Computer Security Conference; 
1989 Oct 10; Baltimore. USA: NIST/NCSC; 1989: 305-319. 

Gasser, Morrie; Lipner, Steve (Secure Systems Development, Digital 
Equipment Corporation). Secure System Development in Industry:  a 
