CACM 27(8)
An interesting idea which provides an enhancement to a simple 
password scheme. It is a simple challenge-response system which 
follows a normal password entry. It might provide better security than 
a simple password but I suspect that in practice the algorithm will 
become well known and thus worthless either because it remains the 
same for a very long time or because the method of distributing the 
new algorithms to the users is not well protected.
