NCSC. Interpretations of the Trusted Computer System Evaluation 
Criteria. USA: NCSC. 
Note: This document contains a number of 'interpretations' of the NCSC 
Trusted Computer Systems Evaluation Criteria (TCSEC), each produced 
by NCSC in response to questions on the application of the TCSEC to 
particular circumstances.  Each interpretation quotes the criteria being 
interpreted, states possible ways in which they could be interpreted in 
a given situation, and then gives an 'accepted interpretation' and a 
rationale for that choice.
