Integrity is taken to mean the correctness and consistency of data. The 
implications of various aspects of integrity are considered, and it is 
concluded that a mandatory integrity policy is required to protect data, 
in addition to the usual policy to protect direct disclosure. It is not yet 
known what this mandatory integrity policy is like.
