Wiseman, S. R. A Garbage Collector for a large distributed address 
space. 1985 Jan 6. 
A new on the fly garbage collection algorithm is presented. It is 
suitable for use in distributed systems, where the address space is 
very large. The time taken to recover garbage is reduced by recursively 
structuring the address space. consideration is given to the practical 
implementation of the algorithm.
