Woo, Thomas Y. C.; Lam, Simon S. (University of Texas). Authentication 
for Distributed Systems. in: COMPUTER. USA: IEEE Computer Society 
Press; 1992 Jan; c1992; 25: pp. 39-52. 
A distributed system is susceptible to a variety of threats mounted by 
intruders. This paper describes a number of protocols to authenticate 
